---
title: PC Parts Tab - Flowchart
---
flowchart TD
    Start([User opens PC Parts Tab])
    
    SelectCategory[Select component category<br/>- CPU<br/>- Memory<br/>- Motherboard<br/>- Video Card<br/>- Case<br/>- Power Supply<br/>- Storage<br/>- Monitor]
    
    LoadAllParts[Load all parts for category]
    ShowFilterOptions[Show filter options<br/>- Price range<br/>- Manufacturer<br/>- Specifications]
    
    UserInput{User input}
    
    %% Filter Path
    ApplyFilters[Apply selected filters]
    FilterResults[Filter parts list]
    
    %% Search Path
    SearchInput[Enter search query]
    SearchResults[Search in parts list]
    
    %% Sort Path
    SelectSort[Select sort option<br/>- Price (Low to High)<br/>- Price (High to Low)<br/>- Name (A-Z)<br/>- Name (Z-A)]
    SortResults[Sort parts list]
    
    DisplayParts[Display parts with pagination]
    
    UserAction{User action}
    
    ViewDetails[View part details<br/>- Specifications<br/>- Images<br/>- Price<br/>- Compatibility info]
    
    LoadMore[Load more parts<br/>(pagination)]
    
    ResetFilters[Reset all filters]
    
    End([End])
    
    Start --> SelectCategory
    SelectCategory --> LoadAllParts
    LoadAllParts --> ShowFilterOptions
    ShowFilterOptions --> UserInput
    
    UserInput -->|Filter| ApplyFilters
    UserInput -->|Search| SearchInput
    UserInput -->|Sort| SelectSort
    UserInput -->|Browse| DisplayParts
    
    ApplyFilters --> FilterResults
    FilterResults --> DisplayParts
    
    SearchInput --> SearchResults
    SearchResults --> DisplayParts
    
    SelectSort --> SortResults
    SortResults --> DisplayParts
    
    DisplayParts --> UserAction
    
    UserAction -->|View Details| ViewDetails
    UserAction -->|Load More| LoadMore
    UserAction -->|Reset| ResetFilters
    UserAction -->|Change Category| SelectCategory
    UserAction -->|Exit| End
    
    ViewDetails --> End
    LoadMore --> DisplayParts
    ResetFilters --> LoadAllParts
